Kate Chiwedu Obilor (amuru 17 Julaị 1985) bu onye Naijiria lagoro ezumike nka n'ihe mgbochi ọ bu onye puru iche na ihe mgbochi 400 mita

Ọ meriri nrite ọla edo na asọmpi West Africa na 2001,  nrite ọla ọcha na 2003 All-Africa Games,  Ọ gwụchara n'ọkwa ise na asọmpi 2006 Africa ma nwetakwa nrite ọla ọcha na mgbagharị 4 × 400 mita na ebe ahụ
Oge kacha mma nkeonwe ya bụ sekọnd 56.50, ọ nwetara na Julaị 2001 na Lagos
